summary:
GOKU COIN - Goku Coin is a decentralized meme coin, community-driven on Ethereum Network. Inspired by the popular anime character, Goku from the legendary Dragon Ball series.

 ABOUT GOKU COIN - Goku is a character and the main protagonist of the Dragon Ball manga series created by Akira Toriyama. He is based on Sun Wukong (known as Son Goku in Japan and Monkey King in the West), a main character of the classic 16th century Chinese novel Journey to the West.

 GOKU COIN TOKENOMICS - TOKEN SUPPLY: 1,000,000,000,000,000 No Team Token, 97% supply for liquidity pool and 3% reserved for CEX listings No Taxes, LP Tokens are burnt and contract ownership is renounced.
